On April 19, 2017, the President signed three resolutions into law. The first resolution, S.J.Res. 30, reappoints Steve Case as a citizen regent of the Board of Regents of the Smithsonian Institution. The second resolution, S.J.Res. 35, appoints Michael Govan as a citizen regent of the Board of Regents of the Smithsonian Institution. Lastly, the third resolution, S.J.Res. 36, appoints Roger W. Ferguson as a citizen regent of the Board of Regents of the Smithsonian Institution.